## ğŸš€ Example Use Cases

### 1. ğŸ› ï¸ Manual append + model roundtrip
```
python
chat = Embr()
chat << user @ "hello"
response = chat > gpt
chat << response
```
### 2. ğŸ§ª Pipe-style chaining
```
python
chat = Embr()
chat = chat << "what is the weather?" | gpt
```
### 3. ğŸ”— Register reducers to the chat
```
python
chat |= gpt | claude | other_ai
chat.apply_reducers()
```
### 4. â“ Conditional reducers
```
python
def gpt_if_question(chat):
if "?" in chat.last.content:
return gpt(chat)


chat |= gpt_if_question
chat << "this is a statement"
chat << "what is this?"
chat.apply_reducers()
```
### 5. ğŸ¤– Multi-agent routing
```
python
chat |= on_call @ gpt | on_call @ images
```
